room_title: Escape room "Vacation Vandals" by Key Quest in San Jose
review: No coherent clues and overall a pretty crappy job just setting things up. You could still tell the room was originally a birthday room. Enough said

room_title: Escape room "Vacation Vandals" by Key Quest in San Jose
review: Decided to try one of those escape rooms with my wife and children. It turned out to be a fun 45-minutes of thinking, communicating and searching for clues. The kids won't stop talking about it, and that's what I call a success!
